Original drawings of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Muller &amp; Troschel" authorityYear="1843" box="[374,489,1905,1932]" class="Asteroidea" family="Echinasteridae" genus="Echinaster" kingdom="Animalia" order="Spinulosida" pageId="23" pageNumber="280" phylum="Echinodermata" rank="species" species="decanus">
